    "Extended Summary": {
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "math",
          "value": "l_p(u, v) = \\left( \\int_{-\\infty}^{+\\infty} |U-V|^p \\right)^{1/p}"
        },
        {
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "value": "p is a positive parameter; p = 1 gives the Wasserstein distance, p = 2 gives the energy distance."
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
